What you need to know:

KCB coach Japheth Munala said most of the players are at better place, save for few who will need to shed weight thanks to festive season."We have just begun training well aware of the fixtures ahead of us. This week we will do more of physicals and proceed to ball work as the days progress, but all in all we are optimistic ahead of the season and we can only hope for the best," said Munala , who doubles up as the national women's team assistant coach.